snippet.title: SNES gaming: Operation Logic Bomb
snippet.description: A game made by Jaleco which was kinda left in the dark. The is a up-view shooter where you gotta make your way through infested base to achieve...some goal! Anyway if you know where to stand and such you'll be making it through the first part pretty easily. There's of course more than just 2 weapons but you gotta find the rest! The music is pretty good in my opinion. Definitely give this game a try if you own a SNES emulator.
